reviewText:
Love this season. Glad they released this. The DVD came in okay. The case is fine. The only problem is that the middle part where it holds the DVD CD, a part is chipped  and it's not holding the disc 2 cd well, it comes off at times. The episodes are in order this time, not like last season dvd.

Disc 1 - Episode 1-4
Disc 2 - Episode 5-7
Disc 3 - Episode 8-10
Disc 4 - Episode 11-13

Great DVD. Thank you for this release!
Please please please release already!
I just love this show don't really care for the the new girls though. I just wish it can hurry and be released on dvd pre ordered it the 16th of october and still waiting. HURRY & RELEASE!!!!
This ladies are just too good
I love the girls. I can relate to all of them on some way. Lady boss, Renee and Big Any are my all time fav babes.
great quality dvd. fast friendly service.
